{
  "stem": "7684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And what was now happened-- this-- one day, the man told me I can go and visit another family what had also Jews hidden.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they lived not far.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was almost next door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I walked to these people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I felt very secure, because I had a passport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every Jew in Holland had a passport with a J in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the underground took the J out from me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I felt very secure when I went there and I walked on the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the minute I come there, the police came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I say, I'm a nurse, and I come and help these people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was another family there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so he said, give me your passport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he hold it to the light.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he could see the J was taken out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I know that that was the end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So this-- what was now happened-- and then he asked me where I was hidden.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't want to tell them that, because, the day before, another family came-- and a couple.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I didn't want to tell him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I thought, these people have to have time to run away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But what was now happened-- these people where I was hidden, were traitors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after me, there were 28 Jews were there, and they all were sent to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nothing was happened to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because-- and always, when Jews were hidden by non-Jews, the-- the-- the-- the people would-- what hide them had to go-- also they went-- were sent to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, after the war, we found out that these people were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, from there, I went to Utrecht.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sudden-- it was in Utrecht, in police station, and I couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
